reviewText: Entertaining enough, but this has nothing to with Tom Clancys Jack Ryan. If you want that - watch The Hunt for Red October. Alec Baldwin was Always the best Ryan.
great movie. good shipping. worth a look
Chris Pine is great as Jack Ryan.  Loved it!

This Is a fun movie to watch. Chris pine is Jack Ryan a CIA recruit is caught a dangerous web of intrigue Spun between his unsuspecing fiancee Keria Knightley and a ruthless russian criminal Kenneth Branagh. Kevin Costner play,s Jack,s boss. This is a Non-stop action thriller ride. You will enjoy this movie. Give it a shot.
Great movie lots of action and believable adventure
